Text: SF Happy HourHello everyone If youre in San Francisco this Friday come join Enlai Rolf Gerry and myself at Kells for a drink We plan to meet there at and everyone is welcome I know it may be tough to choose between Kells in the City and Gordon Biersch in Palo Alto so just let your Friday afternoon location make the choice for you Kells Irish Restaurant Bar is located at Jackson St The cross street is Columbus and their phone number if Hope you can make it Steve
